Subject: [PATCH] drift: move and rename flush planner

---
 CMakeLists.txt                                            | 2 +-
 include/rs/scheduler/{flush_planner.h => plan_composer.h} | 7 +++++--
 src/scheduler/{flush_planner.cpp => plan_composer.cpp}    | 7 ++++---
 src/scheduler/request_scheduler.cpp                       | 4 ++--
 4 files changed, 12 insertions(+), 8 deletions(-)
 rename include/rs/scheduler/{flush_planner.h => plan_composer.h} (53%)
